{"tid":2324320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[傻仔侵粉又睇唔到]特朗普再揚言否決國防授權法案","createTime":"2020-12-14T00:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T02:46:26.000Z","uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aad60e8f9eed129f19ab9bbbc741cad97a82cfd9","tid":2324320,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:39:10.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普再次揚言會否決國防授權法案。<br />\n<br />\n他在Twitter貼文，聲稱中國將是法案的最大贏家，他會否決法案。他沒有進一步解釋。白宮暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n國會參眾兩院早前分別大比數通過2021財政年度的國防授權法案，票數足以推翻特朗普的否決。<br />\n<br />\n法案涉及總值超過7400億美元的國防預算，部分內容亦涉及台灣及香港，包括重申協助台灣維持足夠自我防衛能力，並建立「太平洋威懾倡議」，強化美國在印太防禦能力，又禁止向香港警方出口受管制國防物品、服務和受管制軍需品。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國憲法，若總統行使否決權退回法案，參眾兩院重新表決，若以三分之二多數通過法案，就可以推翻總統的否決權。"},{"pid":"a01e660b70532fae6a2c5c2f6fa49611c50c5004","tid":2324320,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:39:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565098-20201214.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565098-20201214.htm&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725KnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=a394840c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565098-20201214.htm&h=8923315f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565098-20201214.htm</a>"},{"pid":"aa5c2cdba0d3fcca5a8de59041419183ffcf3ccb","tid":2324320,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T00:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻登侵粉死哂去邊"},{"pid":"5dbe82b82da7f5066126f7c910d648c5cf276143","tid":